name: Cammelia Opuntia
description:
--Fig.23--
Cammelia Opuntia is a creature from Naqaya, an exoplanted located 5542 light years from Earth, orbiting the star Nosaxa.
Cammelias live in huge swarms of magestic individuals which can reach up to 5 meters in height. They only feed on sunlight from the 3 suns of its system. As they grow, they develop more and more flower crowns, and by this structure you can tell the age of a Cammelia, who can live an astounding 500 years. Cammelias have a sublime scent that can be sensed light years away, an animals from other solar systems come to polinate them.
